@page "/"

<PageTitle>Index</PageTitle>

<MudText Typo="Typo.h3" GutterBottom="true">Welcome!</MudText>
<MudText Class="mb-8">Hi there! I'm oflords, a passionate coder with a deep love for creating Minecraft plugins. I have been creating them since I was 15, making Minigames for my friends to play and creating unique experiences for the servers I have developed for.</MudText>
<MudText Typo="Typo.h4" GutterBottom="true">Past Servers</MudText>
<MudTimeline>
    <MudTimelineItem Color="Color.Tertiary" Size="Size.Small">
        <ItemOpposite>
            <MudText Color="Color.Tertiary" Typo="Typo.h5">2015</MudText>
        </ItemOpposite>
        <ItemContent>
            <MudText Color="Color.Tertiary" Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">LordRealm</MudText>
            <MudText>My first ever server, consisting of SkyWars and Factions on 1.7-1.8. Closed mid 2016.</MudText>
        </ItemContent>
    </MudTimelineItem>
    <MudTimelineItem Color="Color.Success" Size="Size.Small">
        <ItemOpposite>
            <MudText Color="Color.Success" Typo="Typo.h5">2017</MudText>
        </ItemOpposite>
        <ItemContent>
            <MudText Color="Color.Success" Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">AusHeroes</MudText>
            <MudText>An attempt to released a polished network on 1.7-1.8. Started with SkyWars then transformed into Duels, UHC and later HCF.</MudText>
        </ItemContent>
    </MudTimelineItem>
    <MudTimelineItem Color="Color.Error" Size="Size.Small">
        <ItemOpposite>
            <MudText Color="Color.Error" Typo="Typo.h5">2020</MudText>
        </ItemOpposite>
        <ItemContent>
            <MudText Color="Color.Error" Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">Mythic</MudText>
            <MudText>A rebranding of AusHeroes, offering the same modes on 1.7-1.8. Was partnered with Lunar Client. Sold in 2021.</MudText>
        </ItemContent>
    </MudTimelineItem>
    <MudTimelineItem Color="Color.Info" Size="Size.Small">
        <ItemOpposite>
            <MudText Color="Color.Info" Typo="Typo.h5">2021</MudText>
        </ItemOpposite>
        <ItemContent>
            <MudText Color="Color.Info" Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">Cobalt Club</MudText>
            <MudText>A competitive 1.7-1.8 PotPvP and UHC server with a custom AntiCheat.</MudText>
        </ItemContent>
    </MudTimelineItem>
    <MudTimelineItem Color="Color.Primary" Size="Size.Small">
        <ItemOpposite>
            <MudText Color="Color.Primary" Typo="Typo.h5">2023</MudText>
        </ItemOpposite>
        <ItemContent>
            <MudText Color="Color.Primary" Typo="Typo.h6" GutterBottom="true">Mythic v2</MudText>
            <MudText>The revival of Mythic, made for the latest version of Minecraft! Consists of FFA and Survival.</MudText>
        </ItemContent>
    </MudTimelineItem>
</MudTimeline>